@node "What is it?" "What is it?"
GormanFishtank is a Tamagotchi-like program...  Or is it a virtual pet? Hmm.
Depends on what the definition of a "virtual pet" is, or if there is actually
any difference.

Anyway, said program involves a fish which merrily swims about its bowl, needs
feeding, entertaining and general care and attention.
@endnode

@node "Installation" "Installation"
Just copy the Gorman Fishtank drawer to your hard drive.
@endnode

@node "Requirements" "Requirements"
This program requires:

 - An Amiga (natch)
